// var students = ["avinash", "manoj", "priyanka"]
// var
1. Collect all the chits -> 5 chits ----> (DATA - HOLD) - DONE
2. Created two vote buckets for A and B ( 0, 0 ) ----> (DATA - HOLD) - DONE
3. Take one chit
4. Check response (either A or B) ----> (COMPARISON - CONDITIONAL)
5. Put the chit in the respective bucket ( 1,0 or 0,1 ) ----> (DATA)
6. Go through all the responses and repeat steps 3-5 ----> REPEAT, RECUSIVE, LOOPS
7. Compare both buckets
8. Announce the result
